{
  "stem": "10698.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I talk about it all the time, right?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm so nervous now that I--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were no SS or anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were stapling the staples on-- on-- on the shelves, whatever arrived, for when they were coming out, the-- the trucks to pick certain things up.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was lined up for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we found out that the lag-- the camp is going to be closed up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my brother and-- oh, excuse me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother tried to get, from the other camp-- excuse me-- my sister.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] My sister and her husband, so we were all together, the four of us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was the youngest from the three brothers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What were their names?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What were the boys' names?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my-- [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Edic, ?] the one-- the youngest, and my sister was [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Rosie, ?] and her husband was Abraham [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Zwichel. ?] So we were all together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then, when we kind of thought-- they were kind of telling that they were going to close it up, so my brother and my brother-in-law, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when they went the next time to, you know, pick things for the camp, they were going to look for hiding places.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "While they were away, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they put us on trucks and took us into Warsaw, to the ghetto, to-- it wasn't really ghetto.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, whatever.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It-- the one-- away from people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Meanwhile, I don't know how my brother and my brother-in-law found out that we were loaded on trucks already.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I'll try and be as calm as possible.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because the last time I saw my youngest brother is running after the truck.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He wanted to jump on the truck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was the last time I saw him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After the war, I found out-- we had a friend.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He spoke more-- better Jewish than I did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because I'm the youngest, so mostly, I spoke Polish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That he was hiding with him and his wife and children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And sure enough, somebody squealed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took out the whole family and my brother, and they shot them in the street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Let's see now.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] Either late 20s or early 30s.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Good looking guy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I showed you his picture.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, they wanted to make an actor out of him in the Jewish theater.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then-- so they took us another night into the-- into the Polish-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] it used to be, before the war, they used to have a jail there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they kept us overnight there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from-- Was this in Warsaw?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from there, they took us to Lublin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] That was just for a short time where we were, like, digging ditches or whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was with my sister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All I was concerned about my sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, men and women.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they took us to that place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then when the Warsaw uprising started, and they started to bring some of them over there--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Lublin-- and we wound up all with them together into Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the first death camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By then, we knew already that there is such thing as showers where you don't get water, but gas.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People that did try to run-- to escape, and people started to know what's happening.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where it's supposed to be at every of those death camps, they had a sign, Arbeit macht frei, meaning work makes free.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we undre-- first we had to undress in front of SS men.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mind you, SS men.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Stark naked, walking by, to go in into the shower.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we knew we were going for the sure death.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We went into a shower.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we got some clothes that was full of lice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What did you say to sister?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Do you remember?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, that's it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are done.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when we came out, we have to march again in front of the-- the-- the SS men.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they decided who is going-- no, excuse me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They decided before we went to the shower who is going left or right.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So by the time we came out, we were getting different clothes, shoes that didn't match, and-- Was your hair shaved at the time?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, not-- I never had my hair shaved.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And would you believe that I had blonde curls once upon a time?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is my true color.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm bragging about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But-- so we came out, and we were taken to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
